    dc:creator "Pincheira-Donoso, Daniel; Scolaro, Alejandro" ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "Iguanian species-richness in the Andes of boreal Patagonia: Evidence for an additional new Liolaemus lizard from Argentina lacking precloacal glands (Iguania, Liolaeminae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176299>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176300>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176301>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176302> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176299>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Holotype (a; MLP. R. 5274) and female paratype (b; MLP. R. 5276) of Liolaemus tregenzai in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176299/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176300>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Male (a) and female (b) of Liolaemus tregenzai in life." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176300/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176301>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Variation in morphological traits in the holotype male (a, c, e) and allotype female (b, d, f) of Liolaemus tregenzai. Dorsal body scales in the holotype (a) and in the allotype, ventral body scales in the holotype (c) and in the allotype, and cloacal region in the holotype (e) and in the allotype (f)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176301/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176302>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Map of the North-Western Patagonia of Argentina and Chile, showing the distribution of Liolaemus tregenzai and L. neuquensis (black circle; Copahue Volcano) and L. coeruleus (both black triangles; Pino Hachado, Primeros Pinos)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

